2026-05-08 11:10:33,233 [INFO] [gemini] I have completed the investigation and fix for the 'signal is aborted' error during project save on mobile.
2026-05-08 11:10:33,233 [INFO] [gemini] 
2026-05-08 11:10:33,233 [INFO] [gemini] ### Summary of Changes
2026-05-08 11:10:33,572 [INFO] [gemini] 1.  **Increased API Timeout:** In `client/src/lib/queryClient.ts`, I increased the default timeout in `apiRequest` from 10 seconds to 30 seconds. This provides more headroom for large project states or slow mobile networks.
2026-05-08 11:10:33,572 [INFO] [gemini] 2.  **Retry Logic with Exponential Backoff:**
2026-05-08 11:10:34,185 [INFO] [gemini]     *   **Manual Save:** Updated `useManualSave.ts` to retry aborted requests up to 3 times with exponential backoff ($1s, 2s, 4s$). The retry logic is robust enough to handle partial successes (e.g., if the project was created but the file upload failed, it uses the existing ID on retry).
2026-05-08 11:10:34,527 [INFO] [gemini]     *   **Auto Save:** Updated `useAutoSave.ts` with a similar retry mechanism (up to 2 retries) and added a concurrency guard to prevent redundant saves.
2026-05-08 11:10:34,527 [INFO] [gemini] 3.  **Improved User Feedback:**
2026-05-08 11:10:34,612 [INFO] [gemini]     *   Technical error messages like "signal is aborted" are now replaced with user-friendly descriptions of network/timeout issues.
2026-05-08 11:10:34,738 [INFO] [gemini]     *   A notification toast now informs the user when a save is being retried due to a weak connection.
2026-05-08 11:10:35,107 [INFO] [gemini] 4.  **Awaited Save Operations:** Updated `MobileBottomBar.tsx` and `ProjectActions.tsx` to properly await the `handleSave` promise. This ensures that UI loading indicators (like the spinning loader on the save button) remain active until all retries have completed or finally failed.
2026-05-08 11:10:35,271 [INFO] [gemini] 5.  **Visibility Change Handling:** Ensured that active save operations are allowed to complete when the user switches apps (page becomes hidden) instead of being prematurely aborted.
2026-05-08 11:10:35,271 [INFO] [gemini] 
2026-05-08 11:10:35,427 [INFO] [gemini] The implementation has been documented in `implementation_report.md`.
